<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="tolower" id="tolower">tolower</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cctype&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">tolower</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Converts the given character to lowercase.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "tolower" [1-136] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="parameters" id="parameters">Parameters</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

<code>ch</code> - character to be converted
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "Parameters" [137-192] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="return_value" id="return_value">Return value</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

converted character or <code>ch</code> if no such conversion was possible
</p>

</div>
